wdi2-NY.ADJ.SVNG.CD.def: Adjusted net savings are equal to net national savings plus education expenditure and minus energy depletion, mineral depletion, net forest depletion, and carbon dioxide and particulate emissions damage.
wdi2-NY.ADJ.SVNG.CD.name: Adjusted net savings
wdi2-NY.ADJ.SVNG.CD.source: World Bank staff estimates based on sources and methods described in the World Bank's The Changing Wealth of Nations.
